high_descs: Take the apple in the fridge
Move to apple near the oven
Open the oven put it to the apple set the temperature and take it again
Place the apple on the fridge
anns.task_desc: Take the apple in the table put the apple in oven place the apple on the fridge

high_descs: Turn left. Move forward. Turn to the right. Go towards the fridge.
Open the refrigerator. Grab the apple. Close the refrigerator door.
Turn left. Keep going forward. Turn left. Move to the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the apple on the left side. Close the door. Turn on the microwave for 5 seconds. Open the door, take out the apple.
Turn left, go ahead to the fridge. Turn left. Approach the fridge.
Open the fridge doors. Place the apple on the left side of the second level. Close the fridge doors.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple, heat the apple and take the apple to the fridge.

high_descs: Walk straight and slightly to the left over to the fridge doors.
Open the refrigerator doors, take the apple off of the shelf, and close the doors.
Turn left, walk into the living room, go left and stop next to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the apple inside, close the door and heat, then retrieve the apple and shut the door.
Turn left, walk into the kitchen, and go over to the fridge.
Open up the fridge door, and put the apple on the left side of the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up an apple in the microwave to return to the fridge.
